{"type": "article", "id": 27569, "title": "Jo Malone 推夏日家居系列，以及，COS 夏季女装不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-05-31T10:14:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1936, "name": "香水"}, {"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 1262, "name": "彩虹"}, {"id": 11592, "name": "夏季"}, {"id": 28369, "name": "裙装"}, {"id": 811, "name": "家居"}, {"id": 2603, "name": "香氛"}, {"id": 664, "name": "投资"}, {"id": 248, "name": "COS"}, {"id": 8413, "name": "Jo Malone"}, {"id": 1508, "name": "Net-a-porter"}, {"id": 9191, "name": "Pomellato"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 2180, "name": "Dolce&Gabbana"}, {"id": 28370, "name": "Deckers Brands"}, {"id": 5228, "name": "UGG"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 1802, "name": "Zara"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 66, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702154032RWUpk47yLHNwEe90.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Patrizio-Di-Marco-joins-Dolce-Gabbana,698093.html#.V0zPrYQrJQY\"><b>Gucci 前执政掌管加入 Dolce &amp; Gabbana</b></a>｜持续了几个月的传言已被证实——Gucci 前行政长官、兼任总裁和董事长的 Patrizio Di Marco 加入 Dolce &amp; Gabbana，据意大利媒体介绍，他将担任 Dolce &amp; Gabbana 的高级顾问。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Deckers-Brands-appoints-Dave-Powers-as-CEO,697916.html#.V0zR8YQrJQY\"><b>Deckers Brands 总裁出任集团 CEO</b></a>｜UGG 母公司 Deckers Brands 近日任命公司现任总裁 Dave Powers 为 CEO，5 月 31 日起生效，接替即将退休的 Angel Martinez。在担任总裁前，Powers 任全渠道部门总裁，此前还在 Nike、Timberland、Gap 等担任高级管理职位。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Coach-unveils-Chloe-Grace-Moretz-as-the-face-of-its-fresh-fragrance,697938.html#.V0zPt4QrJQY\"><b>Chloë Grace Moretz 成 Coach 新香水代言人</b></a>｜美国奢侈品牌 Coach 宣布 19 岁女演员 Chloë Grace Moretz 成为旗下女士香水代言人，新广告 9 月推出。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/mergers-acquisitions/ordre-gets-receives-funding-from-taiwanese-group-10439477/\"><b>Ordre 获台湾集团投资</b></a>｜台湾中租控股集团（Chailease）近日对 B2B 平台 Ordre 进行百万美元的战略产权投资，澳大利亚时装周创办人之一 Simon Lock 在 2014 年 11 月建立的网站 Ordre ,如今是聚集了超过 100 位设计师的零售平台。<br></p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/zara-new-in-dress/\">Zara 这一季的裙装不错</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154014fR5VmiTSxZQaDrBU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154015yx5IW0QOq61AopX3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154015eQKiRspGCmOAVlcd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154016upoPgs4LQJU5vdFZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154017PWi2RSg4E9bImOor.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">adidas Originals 推出彩虹配色版本的 Superstar 80 球鞋系列<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/adidas-originals-2016-fall-winter-superstar-80s-pride-sneaker-pack\">“Pride”</a>，6 月 1 日上市：<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154018HU6JC7cM8LuPxGSk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154019GoQI4HO5tnLE6U7h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">巴黎街头时尚品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/pigalle-porter-bags\">Pigalle 与包袋品牌 Porter 合作，推出特别配色系列</a>。每款限量生产 30 件，售价在 189-288 美元。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154019dEJr9aQONnRukFib.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66632124\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154020oQvjmk7851LzKruS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/lookbook/cos-summer-elegant/\">Cos 夏季新品看起来很简约舒适</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154020kOu6qprDo82J5Qml.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154021dUElq74pT6xQerOJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154022Ncm8drzHJV9Ufgps.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154022LiZ8NabAsnrT25oM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154023AZiOxNKJzSIDEY2P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/home-and-living/jo-malone-london-marthe-armitage/\">Jo Malone London 推出限量家居香氛系列</a>，包含蜡烛、沐浴露等，灵感来自夏日的午后，找来艺术家、壁纸设计师  Marthe Armitage 手工绘制礼盒包装：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154024vShzMfWjdx8HbPGI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154024DdKYj8olUxBg9ZXy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154025npNl0oKriMOqd3GY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154026927nfaWdpq0huSZN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>Karl Lagerfeld 品牌与巴西百货商店 Riachuelo 合作 2016 秋冬系列，<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/karl-lagerfeld-riachuelo-fall-winter-2016-campaign-photos/#ixzz4AC4KhnaC\">巴西超模 Isabeli Fontana 拍摄广告</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154026IHQduXKkbg8iwam3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154027DAM70COK5UhVZgzN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6925\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154027p8Sz2aORdqmtxXFB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.36375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154028md7tbY5W3LpcIOrH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>Net-a-porter 与意大利高端珠宝品牌 Pomellato 合作，后者为其<a href=\"http://wwd.com/accessories-news/jewelry/net-a-porter-launches-pomellatos-tango-collection-10439431/\">推出 Tango 独家系列</a>，13 件手镯、耳环等单品。</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154029pUbNDEqGLJumkB35.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64257812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154029axZ1JzwSgHr46hvW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154030IZzgY8k5imjEQbMe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.07128906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154030yAufMVZPCY6spnUO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74902344\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img 